    "subtype": "siege_weapon",
    "text": "The Ustradi long cannon is an incredibly expensive and deadly bombard, designed by the engineers of the Gunworks near Alkenstar in an attempt to craft a slightly more portable version of the feared Maw of Rovagug. Named after the nearby lake, the Ustradi long cannon fires massive, specially made stone spheres propelled by gunpowder explosions in the barrel. Due to its size and weight, it\u2019s difficult to move along its wide runners, especially through muddy terrain. Only a couple of Ustradi long cannons have been built, and no one has yet to commission another as the materials alone cost a small fortune.",
    "traits": [
